  <brief_title>Efficacy and Safety of Repaglinide and Metformin Combination Therapy in Type 2 Diabetes Failing on Oral Anti-diabetic Drugs</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Multi-centre, Single Armed, Open Labelled Trial to Study the Efficacy and Safety Profile of Repaglinide &amp; Metformin Combination Therapy in Chinese Type 2 Diabetics</official_title>
  <sponsors>
