  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This trial is conducted in Asia. The aim of this trial is to evaluate the efficacy and safety
      of repaglinide and metformin combination therapy in Chinese subjects with type 2 diabetes
      inadequately controlled with OAD (oral anti-diabetic drugs).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
